item.title: CVE-2019-6601|2024-09-17T01:31:00.136Z -- f5%20networks%2C%20inc. -- big-ip%20%28aam%29
item.description: In BIG-IP 13.0.0, 12.1.0-12.1.3.7, 11.6.1-11.6.3.2, or 11.5.1-11.5.8, the Application Acceleration Manager (AAM) wamd process used in processing of images and PDFs fails to drop group permissions when executing helper scripts.
